                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                <date>3d Decr/62</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>The <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philada</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Enclosed I forward<lb/> you, as per request, the resolutions<lb/>\n                passed here in honor of <persName>Lady<lb/> Montefiore's</persName> memory. I\n                trust<lb/> you will deem our proceedings of<lb/> sufficient importance<lb/> to\n                insert them in the “Occident.”<lb/> They will no doubt reach you in<lb/> time for\n                the next (<date>Decr</date>) number.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My people lately presented<lb/> me (for the third time) with a<lb/>\n                very liberal testimonial<lb/> accompanied by an address</p>"
                  },
