                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>I mail you with this a paper<lb/> containing the proceedings.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It is long since I have<lb/> had the pleasure of receiving<lb/> a\n                line from you. Though I<lb/> do not publish, like you,<lb/> I assure you my time is\n                so<lb/> taken up that I really cannot<lb/> find leisure for correspondence.<lb/>\n                Perhaps in time this may change.<lb/> You will scarcely believe I have<lb/> not had\n                time yet to complete<lb/>—altho' I have nearly done so—<lb/> the biographical sketch\n                I commenced<lb/> of my late father <add>ע\"ה</add>—but the</p>"
